Danilo Pantić (born 1996), Serbian footballer

Danilo Pennone (born 1963), Italian writer;

Danilo Pérez (born 1965), Panamanian jazz pianist and composer;

Danilo Stojković (1934–2002), Serbian actor

Danilo Šerbedžija (born 1971), Croatian film director

Danilo Veron Bairros (born 1987), Brazilian footballer

Marcos Danilo Padilha (1985–2016), Brazilian footballer

Derived from the Hebrew daniel, means: God is my judge.
